title: Valkyrae x Natsumiii x Lilypichu  - Last Cup of Coffee ♫ Cover
author: Natsumiii
description:
hi please enjoy this cup of coffee with us :3 

• ================ •

Original Song (Lilypichu - Last Cup Of Coffee):
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1aufbwU6s-s

Vocals: 
Valkyrae: https://www.youtube.com/Valkyrae1
Lilypichu: https://www.youtube.com/Lilypichu 

Mixing and mastering:
Tony Aleman: https://twitter.com/instalok_tony

All art in the video made by: Lilypichu
Thumbnail by: 
SmolBean: https://twitter.com/smolbeanfriend_

Lyrics:

[Wendy] Someday we'll have our last conversation
And drink our last cup of coffee

[Rae] Someday we might be 80
And think about the different things we used to say

[All] All the memories of you will just become a ghost
Of a smile [Wendy Harmonies]
[Wendy] caught in the wind
[All] Someday 
[Rae] It'll be the last day

[Lily] I won't forget how it feels to be loved to be remembered by someone as special as you 

[Rae] Someday ([Wendy] someday echo)
[Wendy] I will ([Rae] I will echo) 
[Lily] drink that last cup of coffee with a
[All] Smile (lily does main melody / wendy middle / rae high)
